==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quintan
<hw>Quin"tan</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>quintanus</ets>, fr. <ets>quintus</ets> fifth, <ets>quinque</ets>
five. See <er>Five</er>.]</ety> <def>Occurring as the fifth, after four
others also, occurring every fifth day, reckoning inclusively; <as>as, a
<ex>quintan</ex> fever</as>.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>An intermittent fever which returns every fifth
day, reckoning inclusively, or in which the intermission lasts three
days.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quintel</ent>⟦br⟧
